message: Hi Bob, I propose a 60-40 split in my favor. This is a fair offer considering we both need to reach an agreement, and you'll get a substantial portion right away without risking inflation.

Alice, I propose that you get $70 and I get $30. I understand you might prefer to wait and make your own proposal later, but further delay will cost me due to inflation.
